Key.Original: All units except the driver must have left the vehicle in order to build the FOB.
Key.English: All units except the driver must have left the vehicle in order to build the FOB.
Key.German: Um die VOB aufbauen zu können müssen alle Einheiten bis auf den Fahrer das Fahrzeug verlassen haben.

Key.Original: The engine must be switched off and the vehicle has to be stopped to build up the FOB.
Key.English: The engine must be switched off and the vehicle has to be stopped to build up the FOB.
Key.German: Der Motor muss ausgeschaltet sein und das Fahrzeug muss stehen, um die VOB aufzubauen.

Key.Original: You have started the construction of a FOB near %1.
Key.English: You have started the construction of a FOB near %1.
Key.German: Sie haben den Aufbau einer VOB in der Nähe von %1 begonnen.

Key.Original: You have completed the construction of a FOB near %1.
Key.English: You have completed the construction of a FOB near %1.
Key.German: Sie haben den Bau einer VOB in der Nähe von %1 abgeschlossen.

Key.Original: %1 starts to build up a Forward Operating Base near %2.
Key.English: %1 starts to build up a Forward Operating Base near %2.
Key.German: %1 hat den Aufbau einer VOB in der Nähe von %2 begonnen.

Key.Original: A Forward Operating Base has been built up near %1.
Key.English: A Forward Operating Base has been built up near %1.
Key.German: In der Nähe von %1 wurde eine vorgeschobene Operationsbasis fertiggestellt.

Key.Original: You have begun dismantling the FOB near 1%.
Key.English: You have begun dismantling the FOB near 1%.
Key.German: Sie haben den Rückbau der VOB in der Nähe von %1 begonnen.

Key.Original: You have complete the dismantling of the FOB near 1%.
Key.English: You have complete the dismantling of the FOB near 1%.
Key.German: Sie haben den Rückbau der VOB in der Nähe von %1 abgeschlossen.

Key.Original: %1 starts to dismount the Forward Operating Base near %2.
Key.English: %1 starts to dismount the Forward Operating Base near %2.
Key.German: %1 beginnt mit dem Abbau Ihrer VOB in der Nähe von %2.

Key.Original: Your FOB near %1 has been dismounted.
Key.English: Your FOB near %1 has been dismounted.
Key.German: Ihre VOB in der Nähe von %1 wurde abgebaut.
